FBIS4-35339 "drnes104_j_94054" FBIS-NES-94-104 Daily Report 29 May 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Citizens Urged Not To Respond To Missile Attacks Citizens Urged Not To Respond To Missile Attacks EA2905190594 Aden Democratic Republic of Yemen Radio Network in English 1600 GMT 29 May 94 EA2905190594 Aden Democratic Republic of Yemen Radio Network in English 1600 GMT 29 May 94 English BFN [Text] An official source in the Interior Ministry in the capital, Aden, has appealed to the citizens in the governorate not to open fire unnecessarily when our land defenses carry out their national duty of repelling the missiles which are launched against the populated targets. He pointed out that random opening of fire causes more inconvenience to citizens.
